DESCRIPTION:We will be sending postcards to swing states to combat disinfo
 rmation as we head into the 2026 midterm elections. These are the states t
 hat provide us the best opportunities to flip the House and Senate in 2026
  and put real controls on the Trump regime.\n\nSnacks and water will be pr
 ovided. We will be in **Meeting Room B.**\n\nIf you can\, please bring 10 
 postcard stamps or make a small donation to our stamp fund. If you can’t
 \, it is not a problem. What is most important is all of us joining togeth
 er to save our democracy and to come out better on the other side.\n\n### 
 Photography and Video Policy\nISCI may take photos or videos at meetings a
 nd events to document\, share\, and promote our activities. When taking ph
 otos or videos\, ISCI representatives will do their best to seek explicit 
